==English==
===Noun===
'''postposition''' (''plural:'' [[postpositions]])

#{{grammar}}: A class of words in languages such as Hindi, Japanese and Finno-Ugric languages (Estonian, Finnish) which serves the same purpose as [[preposition]]s but comes '''after''' the noun.

